class Solution {
    public int hammingDistance(int x, int y) {
        int xor = x ^ y;
        int count = 0;
        while (xor != 0) {
            count += xor & 1;
            xor >>= 1;
        }
        return count;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(log n)
space complexity: O(1)
